	   <tr><td colspan=2>Depending on where you are, there are different ways to get quick cash.  When I was a newbie, I got a port near Crushbone and went there.  In Crushbone you can get things called CB Belts, you fill up a back pack with those, and they got for a 1pp per belt, there are also "CB Pads" in there, which are Crushbone Shoulder Pads, that go for 2pp-4pp depending on server, etc.  When you get to 20 or so I would definately check out Lake of Ill Omen.  The Sarnaks, Goblins, Skeletons there, drop on average at least 1-2pp.  I wouldn't be worrying about int items early in the game, they do nothing for you.  Get items that actually give you mana instead.<br><br>Skildoroth<br>Level 30 Iksar Necromancer<br>Sarryn<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
