	   <tr><td colspan=2>For great exp and cash at level 12 go to WK and Hunt Misty Storyswapper, she is just north of the Qeynos Hills entrance outside of one of the building.  U can do her at 12, but it can be tricky.<br><br>There are a couple way you can do her.  But the easiest way is to fear kite. Send pet and then cast darkenss right away.  Cast til it sticks then fear and heatblood, leach, fear again, med.  U might have to tap once or twice, but she does not have a lot of HP for her level.<br><br>You will make level 13 very quicky.  Like in 2-3 hours and will get and average of 2-3pp of loot each drop ( I have looted over 4pp with a good cash drop and 2 pieces of raw hide with the madolin that drops each kill). Also u can camp her all the way to 18 if u like.  <br><br>I tried Oasis from level 16 to almost 18 and was not excited about the loot and exp wasnt as good as I had hoped.  Came back and hunted Misty for the last yellow bubble, and even a that level, I got as good of exp hunting her as I did in Oasis.<br><br>Another bonus is that Qeynos Hills zone is not too fr away so if things look bad you can try and make it to zone.<br><br>At 18 U an hunt a bard in NK at wizzy spires.  She is really tough at 18, but can be done.  Exp is good and loot is not bad.  Hunt her til 20-22 then try and get hermit in SK. At 24, if u get you 24 pet spell, try the single treant spawn in WK til 29-30.<br><br><br>Kalypto<br>51 necro<br>&nbsp;<br>Kalypto</td></tr>
