	   <tr><td colspan=2>well you're not totally wrong, it is ramdom whether they resist or not, but as w/ chanters and their mezzes our cha does have an effect on the fears, though not a big one.  if a nec gets his cha down to about 20 or lower i've found that fears are resisted a lot less, also if we get our cha really high.  but IMHO taking your cha down is NEVER a good idea because feign death, the savior of all necs, is cha based too... the higher your cha the less likey a mob is to see through it.  so in short our cha does affect some of our spells, but not to an extent we have to worry about at all most of the time<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
